lead_paragraph: The Wallabies believe they are on the right track after building depth in 2016, despite slumping to nine losses in a season where they thought they would close the gap on world champions New Zealand and win back the Bledisloe Cup.

headline.print_headline: Wallabies Hoping to Benefit From Building Depth in 2016
